{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "本章通过多条故事线展开江湖众生相。叶翔与孟星魂在树下饮酒叙旧，叶翔倾诉杀人三十次后的深重疲倦与精神崩溃，告诫孟星魂不要重蹈覆辙。方幼苹因妻子朱青与毛威私通而痛苦不堪。张老头的女儿被江家兄弟欺辱，徐青松判案不公。铁成刚被黄山三友诬陷追杀，逃至孙玉伯处求助。黛黛与小武的恋情被万鹏王发现。孙玉伯寿辰之日，孟星魂化名陈志明混入贺客观察目标。老伯处理各方求助，韩棠前来道别。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这么早就清醒了，可不是件好事，赶快来喝一杯。",
      "tone": "嘶哑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这不是好酒，我知道你喝不惯的，但无论多坏的酒，总比没有酒好。",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "高老大还肯让我喝这样的酒，已经算很对得起我了，其实像我这样的人，现在只配喝马尿。",
      "tone": "凄凉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "现在我们见面的机会越来越少，我并不怪你。你就算看不起我，也是应该的，若不是你，我已死在杨玉麟手上。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "其实那次我早就知道你会在后面跟着来的，所以我……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "那次我根本就不应该去的。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你知道高老大叫我跟着你，知道她对你已不放心，所以你对自己没有信心了，我若不去，你一定可以杀死杨玉麟。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你错了，那次我去杀雷老的时候，已知道以后永远也没法子杀人了。",
      "tone": "凄凉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "雷老三只不过是个放印子钱的恶霸，你平时最恨这种人，我一直奇怪，那次你为什么居然下不了手？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我也不知道为了什么，我只是忽然觉得很疲倦，疲倦得什么事都不想去做，那种感觉你也许不会懂的。",
      "tone": "苦涩",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我懂。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你懂？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我已杀过十一个人。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知道我杀过多少人？",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我杀了三十个，不多不少，整整三十个。",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你将来一定也要杀这么多的人，也许还要多些，因为你非杀不可，否则你会变成我这样子。",
      "tone": "悲凉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "每个人，都有自己的命运，大多数人都在受着命运的摆布，只有很少人能反抗，能改变自己的命运。我只恨我自己为什么不是这种人。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "但我也曾有过机会的。",
      "tone": "微光",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你有过？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "有一次，我遇见过一个人，她愿意不顾一切来帮助我，那时我若肯不顾一切跟她走，现在也许活得很好——就算死，也会死得很好。",
      "tone": "惆怅",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么当时没有那么做呢？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "那也许因为我是个又愚蠢又混蛋、又胆小的呆子，我不敢。",
      "tone": "黯然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你不是不敢，是不忍。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不忍，不忍更呆，我只希望你莫要跟我一样呆。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "机会只有一次，错过了就永不再来。但每个人一生中都至少会有这么样一次机会的，我求你，等机会来的时候，千万莫要错过。",
      "tone": "恳切",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你是不是又有事要做了？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这次你要杀的是谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "孙玉伯。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "是江南的孙玉伯？",
      "tone": "震惊",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我见过。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "他是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他是个怎么样的人……没有人能说得出，我只知道一件事",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我绝不会去杀他！",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我也只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我非杀他不可——",
      "tone": "决绝",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "方幼苹",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qing",
      "text": "你出去干什么去了？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "找人。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "方幼苹",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qing",
      "text": "找谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "当然是去找毛威。",
      "tone": "轻蔑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "方幼苹",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qing",
      "text": "毛威，你……你又去找他干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "你想知道我去干什么，是不是？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "他也喝酒，但却不像你，他就算醉了也行。",
      "tone": "嘲笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "方幼苹",
      "listener": "char_zhu_qing",
      "text": "我杀了你！",
      "tone": "暴怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "你杀吧，你只有本事杀我，你若敢去杀他，我才佩服你。",
      "tone": "嘲笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "别打我的脸……",
      "tone": "尖叫",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "来吧，我知道你真正想要的是这个，我虽然陪过了他，却还是可以再陪你，陪你用不着费力。",
      "tone": "浪笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "我知道你一喝醉就不行，我要去睡了，千万莫要来吵我，因为我要睡得好，明天才有精神去见他！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qing",
      "speaker_name": "朱青",
      "listener": "char_fang_ping",
      "text": "除非你杀了他，否则我天天都要去找他的！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "张老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也有二十一两银子，带你的姐姐，带你妹妹来，我也要……",
      "tone": "嘶喊",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_tou",
      "text": "这件事是你们做的？说实话！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "想不到你们竟会做出这种事，你父亲对你们的教训，难道你们全都忘了？我身为你们父亲的兄弟，少不得要替他教训教训你们，你们服不服？",
      "tone": "怒道",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江风",
      "listener": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "text": "服。",
      "tone": "顺从",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你们的行为虽可恶，总算还勇于认错，没有在我面前说谎，年轻人只要肯认错，就还有救药，而且幸好张姑娘所受的伤不算太严重……",
      "tone": "缓和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "我只问你们，以后还敢再做这种事不？",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_ping",
      "speaker_name": "江平",
      "listener": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "text": "不敢了。",
      "tone": "顺从",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "念在你们初犯，又勇于认错，这次我特别从轻发落，罚你们在这里做七天苦工，每天三两工钱，全都算张姑娘受伤的费用。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_tou",
      "text": "若不是你女儿招蜂引蝶，他们兄弟也不敢做这种事，否则他们为什么没有对别的女孩子这么做，这堡里的女孩子又不止你女儿一个。",
      "tone": "冷漠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_song",
      "speaker_name": "徐青松",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_tou",
      "text": "快回去教训你自己的女儿，少在这里发疯！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "你们好大的胆子！",
      "tone": "怒道",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "我知道你们一向胡做非为，却还是想不到你们竟敢做出这种事。",
      "tone": "沉脸",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "还敢说谎？",
      "tone": "怒容",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "不是你们做的，是谁做的？你们刀上的血还没有擦干净！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "这件事全是我做的，他们什么都不知道！",
      "tone": "大喊",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "你要我放了他们？",
      "tone": "冷问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "只要你放了他们，我一个字都不说，我保证！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个都不能放走，杀！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能让他走，杀！这五个我一人对付就已足够。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "铁成刚，你可听到了你兄弟的惨呼声？你竞不管他们？你这样算什么朋友？",
      "tone": "怒道",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "咱们还是先退出去，他反正跑不了的。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "尸身多少？",
      "tone": "冷问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_shi",
      "text": "八十五。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "铁成刚还没有死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_shi",
      "text": "他还没有死。",
      "tone": "点头",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "他不能不死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_shi",
      "text": "他只怕已经由这地道中逃了出去。",
      "tone": "难看",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_shi",
      "text": "他是段老四的亲戚，当然到这里来过，所以知道这条地道。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_shi",
      "text": "当然要追，就算追到天涯海角，也不能让他逃掉。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "小武，你本不该这么喜欢我的，也不应该对我这么好。",
      "tone": "幽叹",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "小武",
      "listener": "char_dai_dai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "因为我不配。",
      "tone": "黯然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "你知道，我只不过是人家的一个小丫头，我全身上下都是人家的，人家要我死，我就不能活。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "小武",
      "listener": "char_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，千万莫要再说这种话，只要你的心是我的，我的心是你的，我们什么都不必怕。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "我不怕别的，只担心我们的事有一天被人家发现了。",
      "tone": "黯然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "老爷子是绝不会让我跟你在一起的，你总该知道他对下人是多么严，他若知道这件事……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "小武",
      "listener": "char_dai_dai",
      "text": "我不会让任何人来拆散我们，绝不会……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "我知道你是“镇武镖局”武老刀的儿子，看在他曾经替我做过事的份儿上，今天饶你不死，但你下次要是还敢再到这里，我将你五马分尸！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬他回去，告诉武老刀，他若是想要他的儿子，就不要放他出门！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你听过陈志明这名字没有？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "这两年你常到外面去走动，怎么会没听过这名字？",
      "tone": "皱眉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他绝不是著名的人！",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "奇怪，像这么样一个年轻人，怎么会是无名之辈？",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "也许他运气不好。",
      "tone": "随意",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "等会你去问问律香川，也许他知道。",
      "tone": "吩咐",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "韩棠来了，已经在外面等了很久，要亲自向你老人家道别。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不该来的！",
      "tone": "沉脸",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既然来了，就让他进来吧！",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "这一向你还好？",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "还没有女人？",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "你应该找个女人的",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我不信任女人。",
      "tone": "冷漠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "太信任女人固然不好，太不信任女人也同样不好，女人可以使男人安定。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "女人也可以使男人发疯。",
      "tone": "冷漠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "你看到了小方？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他没有看到我。",
      "tone": "冷漠",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算是有人看到我，也不认得。",
      "tone": "讥消",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可以走了，明年你不来也无妨，我知道你的心意。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_tang",
      "speaker_name": "韩棠",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "明年我还要来，每年我只出来一次。",
      "tone": "一字字",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_han_tang",
      "text": "我房里没有人，你若愿意留下来喝杯酒，我陪你。",
      "tone": "客气",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你很同情他？",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "能同情别人，是件好事，你可以同情任何人",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "却不能同情他。",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "因为你若同情他，他就会发疯。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他究竟是个怎样的人？以前做过什么事？",
      "tone": "忍不住",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你不必知道他是个怎样的人，有很多事你都不必知道。",
      "tone": "沉脸",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "垂首",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他做过的事以前绝没有人做过，以后只怕也没有人能做但我不妨告诉你",
      "tone": "长叹",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老伯。",
      "tone": "嘶喊",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "是你，你怎么变成这个样子的？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "不用怕，到了这里，你什么都不用怕了，谁都不用怕了，在这里绝没有人敢碰你一根毫毛！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "这句话你不该说的。",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "你也许还不知道他是个杀人的凶手，而且杀的是他自己的舅父。",
      "tone": "冷道",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "我只知道他是我的朋友，而且受了伤，只知道他信任我，所以才会到这里来，所以谁都休想将他带走。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "找你的父亲来，我们要跟他说话。",
      "tone": "沉脸",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "我父亲说的话也一样，就算天王老子也休想从这里带走我们的朋友！",
      "tone": "青筋凸起",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_jian",
      "text": "好大胆，你父亲也不敢对我们如此无礼！",
      "tone": "怒道",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_jian",
      "speaker_name": "孙剑",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "你错了，他的无礼是遗传，他父亲也许比他更无礼。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "你怎知……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "我当然知道，因为，我就是他父亲。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "孙施主与贫道等素不相识，所以才会如此说话。",
      "tone": "缓和",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_yun",
      "text": "无论你们是谁，我说的话，都一样。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_quan",
      "speaker_name": "一泉道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "久闻孙玉伯做事素来公道，今日怎会包庇凶手？",
      "tone": "变色",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_quan",
      "text": "就算他是凶手，也得等他伤好了再说，何况谁也不能证明他是凶手。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我们亲眼所见，难道会假？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_yun",
      "text": "你们亲眼所见，我并未见到，我只知他若是凶手，就绝不敢到这里来！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_yun",
      "speaker_name": "一云道人",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "你连黄山三友的话，都不信？",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_yi_yun",
      "text": "黄山三友是人，铁成刚也是人，在这里无论谁都一样有权说话，我要听听他说的。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "铁成刚",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他们才是凶手，我有证据，他们知道我有证据，所以才一定要杀我灭口！",
      "tone": "大喊",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_tie_cheng_gang",
      "text": "证据在哪里？",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一石道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀人者死，用不着再说，杀！",
      "tone": "尖声",
      "chapter": 2
    }
  ],
